"{\"correct\": \"no\", \"explanation\": \"The code incorrectly uses the rc parameter in sns.set_style(). The rc parameter is not valid for set_style() as it only accepts style names. The correct way to customize styles is to use set_context() for context-related parameters and set_style() for style-related parameters without the rc argument.\", \"patch\": \"14c14\\n< sns.set_style(rc=style_dict)\\n---\\n> sns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n\"}"